
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Seascape Commerce — Navigate the Future of Commerce</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg: #05070F;
    --panel: #0E1630;
    --panel-2: #131C3D;
    --orange: #FF5A1F;
    --orange-dim: #B8420F;
    --cream: #F4D9A8;
    --cyan: #3EE6E0;
    --slate: #8B97B8;
    --line: rgba(139,151,184,0.16);
    --display: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
    --body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}

  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}

  body{
    background: var(--bg);
    color: #E7ECFB;
    font-family: var(--body);
    overflow-x:hidden;
    position:relative;
  }

  /* ===== Starfield canvas background ===== */
  #starfield{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;
    z-index:0; pointer-events:none;
  }

  /* ===== Fixed top-left brand badge ===== */
  #brand-badge{
    position:fixed;
    top:20px; left:20px;
    z-index:1000;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:14px;
    padding:10px 18px 10px 10px;
    background: rgba(14,22,48,0.55);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,90,31,0.08), 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    transition: box-shadow .4s ease, border-color .4s ease;
  }
  #brand-badge::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute; inset:-1px;
    border-radius:14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,90,31,0.35), transparent 40%, rgba(62,230,224,0.25));
    z-index:-1;
    opacity:.6;
    filter: blur(6px);
    animation: badgePulse 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes badgePulse{
    0%,100%{opacity:.35;}
    50%{opacity:.75;}
  }
  #brand-badge img{
    height:46px;
    width:46px;
    object-fit:contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(255,90,31,0.45));
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  #brand-badge .brand-text{
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight:900;
    font-size:38px;
    line-height:1;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream) 0%, var(--orange) 60%, var(--cream) 100%);
    background-size: 200% auto;
    -webkit-background-clip:text;
    background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    color:transparent;
    animation: shimmer 5s linear infinite;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  #brand-badge .brand-sub{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:9px;
    letter-spacing:3px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-top:2px;
    opacity:.8;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer{
    0%{background-position: 0% center;}
    100%{background-position: 200% center;}
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px){
    #brand-badge .brand-text{font-size:26px;}
    #brand-badge img{height:34px;width:34px;}
  }

  /* ===== AI Wayfinder chatbox (below badge) ===== */
  #wayfinder{
    position:fixed;
    top:90px; left:20px;
    z-index:999;
    width:300px;
    max-width: calc(100vw - 40px);
    background: rgba(10,16,36,0.7);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    overflow:hidden;
    transition: max-height .4s ease;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-header{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    padding:12px 14px;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-bottom:1px solid transparent;
  }
  #wayfinder.open .wf-header{
    border-bottom-color: var(--line);
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-orb{
    width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--cyan), #0E6E6A 70%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(62,230,224,0.7);
    flex-shrink:0;
    animation: orbPulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes orbPulse{
    0%,100%{transform:scale(1); box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(62,230,224,0.5);}
    50%{transform:scale(1.15); box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(62,230,224,0.9);}
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-title{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:1.5px;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    flex:1;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-title small{
    display:block;
    font-size:9px;
    color: var(--slate);
    letter-spacing:1px;
    margin-top:2px;
    text-transform:none;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-toggle{
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size:14px;
    transition: transform .3s ease;
  }
  #wayfinder.open .wf-toggle{ transform: rotate(180deg); }

  #wayfinder .wf-body{
    max-height:0;
    overflow:hidden;
    transition: max-height .4s ease;
  }
  #wayfinder.open .wf-body{
    max-height:380px;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-messages{
    height:230px;
    overflow-y:auto;
    padding:12px 14px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:10px;
    font-size:12.5px;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-messages::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;}
  #wayfinder .wf-messages::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background: rgba(62,230,224,0.3); border-radius:3px;}

  #wayfinder .msg{
    max-width:85%;
    padding:8px 11px;
    border-radius:10px;
    animation: msgIn .3s ease;
  }
  @keyframes msgIn{
    from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px);}
    to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
  }
  #wayfinder .msg.bot{
    align-self:flex-start;
    background: rgba(62,230,224,0.08);
    border:1px solid rgba(62,230,224,0.18);
    color:#D9F7F5;
  }
  #wayfinder .msg.user{
    align-self:flex-end;
    background: rgba(255,90,31,0.12);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,90,31,0.25);
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-quick{
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;
    padding:0 14px 12px;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-quick button{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:.5px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    background: rgba(62,230,224,0.06);
    border:1px solid rgba(62,230,224,0.25);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:5px 10px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition: all .2s ease;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-quick button:hover{
    background: rgba(62,230,224,0.18);
    color:#fff;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-input-row{
    display:flex; gap:6px;
    padding:10px 12px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-input-row input{
    flex:1;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:8px 10px;
    color:#fff;
    font-size:12px;
    font-family: var(--body);
    outline:none;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-input-row input:focus{ border-color: var(--cyan); }
  #wayfinder .wf-input-row button{
    background: var(--orange);
    color:#1A0A02;
    border:none;
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:0 13px;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:12px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition: background .2s ease;
  }
  #wayfinder .wf-input-row button:hover{ background: var(--cream); }

  @media (max-width:640px){
    #wayfinder{ width: calc(100vw - 40px); top:80px; }
  }

  /* ===== Layout helpers ===== */
  .wrap{
    max-width:1240px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  section{
    position:relative;
    z-index:1;
    padding:120px 0;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:4px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:'';
    width:36px; height:1px;
    background: var(--cyan);
    opacity:.6;
  }
  h1,h2,h3{
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight:900;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    line-height:1.05;
  }
  h2{
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  p{
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size:16px;
    line-height:1.7;
    max-width:640px;
  }
  .reveal{
    opacity:0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity .8s ease, transform .8s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible{
    opacity:1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    text-decoration:none;
    color:#1A0A02;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream), var(--orange));
    padding:15px 28px;
    border-radius:6px;
    font-weight:700;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
    transition: transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255,90,31,0.5);
  }
  .btn:hover{
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,90,31,0.35);
  }
  .btn.ghost{
    background:transparent;
    color: var(--cyan);
    border:1px solid rgba(62,230,224,0.4);
  }
  .btn.ghost:hover{
    background: rgba(62,230,224,0.08);
    box-shadow:none;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* ===== About panels ===== */
  .panel{
    background: var(--panel);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:28px;
    transition: border-color .3s ease, transform .3s ease;
  }
  .panel:hover{
    border-color: rgba(62,230,224,0.35);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .panel-icon{
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-size:20px;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }

  /* ===== Solution cards ===== */
  .sol-card{
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--panel-2), var(--panel));
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:32px;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
    transition: transform .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
  }
  .sol-card::after{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    top:-50%; right:-50%;
    width:200px; height:200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,90,31,0.12), transparent 70%);
    opacity:0;
    transition: opacity .4s ease;
  }
  .sol-card:hover::after{ opacity:1; }
  .sol-card:hover{
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(255,90,31,0.3);
  }
  .sol-num{
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size:42px;
    font-weight:900;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px var(--orange);
    opacity:.7;
  }
  .card-link{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:18px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:1.5px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-decoration:none;
    transition: color .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
  }
  .card-link:hover{ color: var(--cream); transform: translateX(4px); display:inline-block; }

  /* ===== Stats ===== */
  .stat-block{
    position:relative;
    padding:32px 16px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    background: rgba(14,22,48,0.3);
  }
  .stat-num{
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 80px);
    font-weight:900;
    display:inline;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream), var(--orange));
    -webkit-background-clip:text;
    background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    color:transparent;
  }
  .stat-suffix{
    display:inline;
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 80px);
    font-weight:900;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }
  .stat-label{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:3px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color: var(--slate);
    margin-top:10px;
  }

  /* ===== Timeline ===== */
  .timeline{
    border-left:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-left:32px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:36px;
  }
  .tl-item{ position:relative; }
  .tl-dot{
    position:absolute;
    left:-39px; top:4px;
    width:14px; height:14px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background: var(--bg);
    border:2px solid var(--cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(62,230,224,0.5);
  }
  .tl-year{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    color: var(--orange);
    margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .tl-text{
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size:14px;
    line-height:1.6;
    max-width:420px;
  }

  /* ===== Focus cards ===== */
  .focus-card{
    background: var(--panel);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:30px;
    transition: border-color .3s ease, transform .3s ease;
  }
  .focus-card:hover{
    border-color: rgba(255,90,31,0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .focus-label{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:2.5px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom:14px;
  }

  /* ===== Why us rows ===== */
  .why-row{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:40px 0;
    max-width:760px;
  }
  .why-row:first-of-type{ border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .why-tag{
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:2.5px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .cta-panel{
    max-width:760px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:64px 40px;
    border:1px solid rgba(62,230,224,0.25);
    border-radius:24px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(62,230,224,0.08), transparent 60%), var(--panel);
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .cta-panel h2{ font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 44px); }
  .cta-panel p{ max-width:520px; }

  /* ===== Footer ===== */
  footer{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    position:relative;
    z-index:1;
  }
  .foot-link{
    color: var(--slate);
    text-decoration:none;
    transition: color .2s ease;
  }
  .foot-link:hover{ color: var(--cyan); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<canvas id="starfield"></canvas>

<!-- BRAND BADGE -->
<div id="brand-badge">
  <img src="assets/logo-icon.png" alt="Seascape Commerce logo">
  <div>
    <div class="brand-text">Seascape</div>
    <div class="brand-sub">Commerce // Orbital Ops</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- AI WAYFINDER -->
<div id="wayfinder">
  <div class="wf-header" onclick="document.getElementById('wayfinder').classList.toggle('open')">
    <div class="wf-orb"></div>
    <div class="wf-title">Wayfinder AI<small>Ask me where to go</small></div>
    <div class="wf-toggle">▾</div>
  </div>
  <div class="wf-body">
    <div class="wf-messages" id="wf-messages">
      <div class="msg bot">Hey — I'm Wayfinder. Tell me what you're trying to do and I'll point you to the right part of Seascape Commerce.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wf-quick">
      <button onclick="wfAsk('I need fulfillment help')">Fulfillment</button>
      <button onclick="wfAsk('Show me AI insights')">AI Insights</button>
      <button onclick="wfAsk('I want a website built')">Web Dev</button>
      <button onclick="wfAsk('How do I get started?')">Get Started</button>
    </div>
    <div class="wf-input-row">
      <input type="text" id="wf-input" placeholder="Type a question..." onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')wfSend()">
      <button onclick="wfSend()">Send</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section id="hero" style="padding-top:160px; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center;">
  <div class="wrap" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:60px; align-items:center; width:100%;">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Innovate · Grow · Sustain</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 84px); margin-bottom:24px;">
        Chart a course<br>
        <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--orange)); -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; color:transparent;">through commerce.</span>
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:18px; max-width:520px;">
        Seascape Commerce gives entrepreneurs an AI-driven command deck for online business — fulfillment, marketing, and storefront engineering, all routed through one intelligent system.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; margin-top:36px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn">Launch Your Store →</a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn ghost">Explore the Mission</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="hero-visual" style="position:relative; aspect-ratio:1/1;">
      <canvas id="route-canvas" style="width:100%; height:100%;"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ABOUT / VISION ============ -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center; max-width:760px; margin:0 auto 80px;">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;"><span style="margin-right:0;">Who We Are</span></div>
      <h2>Vision and mission, charted</h2>
      <p style="margin:0 auto;">Seascape Commerce is a complete operating system for online business — combining AI-driven tools, social commerce integration, and fulfillment infrastructure into a single, coordinated platform.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap:24px;">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-icon">◈</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px;">Dedicated Communication</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">A direct line to your team — no ticket queues, no runaround. Just a coordinated crew that knows your store.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-icon">◈</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px;">Tailored Web Development</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">Storefronts built around how your customers actually shop, not a recycled template.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-icon">◈</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px;">Marketing Management</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">Campaigns planned, launched, and measured — so growth isn't guesswork.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:60px; text-align:center;">
      <a href="#solutions" class="btn ghost">Learn More About Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ SOLUTIONS ============ -->
<section id="solutions" style="background:linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(14,22,48,0.4), transparent);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal" style="max-width:640px; margin-bottom:64px;">
      <div class="eyebrow">Our Solutions</div>
      <h2>Tailored for your trajectory</h2>
      <p>Three integrated systems, working in sync to simplify and accelerate how your business operates online.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap:24px;">
      <div class="sol-card">
        <div class="sol-num">01</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:22px; margin:18px 0 12px;">AI-Powered Insights</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">Unlock your business potential with intelligent data analysis — demand forecasting, customer behavior, and performance tracking built into one dashboard.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="card-link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-card">
        <div class="sol-num">02</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:22px; margin:18px 0 12px;">Seamless Fulfillment</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">Hassle-free order management and fulfillment, tailored to your volume and shipping footprint — from first order to scale.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="card-link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="sol-card">
        <div class="sol-num">03</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:22px; margin:18px 0 12px;">Social Commerce Integration</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;">Tap into social platforms and micro-influencer networks to grow sales through channels your customers already trust.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="card-link">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ STATS ============ -->
<section id="stats">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap:24px; text-align:center;">
      <div class="stat-block">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="98">0</div>
        <div class="stat-suffix">%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-block">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="42">0</div>
        <div class="stat-suffix">+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Team Members</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-block">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="30">0</div>
